snippet.title: The Occultist | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2092840/
https://store.playstation.com/de-de/concept/10012077
"Images are engraved in my mind that would make any man tremble in fear... but I am not just any man. I am The Occultist.”
Accompany Alan Rebels on his most terrifying occult investigation yet, in this spine-chilling horror experience. Coming 2025 to PC and Consoles!
